Au7--lai5 Chu2-jit8-oh8 soah, in chiu7 chhoa7 khi3 hu3 toa7-lang5 e5 le2-pai3, hit-jit8 chin hoaN-hi2, tng2-khi3 na2 chhin-chhiuN7 u7 be7 kong2--tit e5 hoaN-hi2 kap kam2-kek ti7 in e5 sim-lai7 e5 khoan2. Keh cha2-khi2 chiu7-si7 pai3-it, Siu3-jiong5 kap i e5 sio2-ti7 Bun5-hiong5 chiu7 kap i e5 chhong-iu2 Giok8-ki saN-si5 to3-khi3 in e5 pun2 sou2-chai7; ng3-bang7 koh bo5 loa7-ku2 in beh koh ti7 Lu2-oh8 lai5 cho3-hoe2, chiu7 an2-ni tai7-ke chiam7-si5 li7-piat8. 
Liat8-ui7 hiaN-ti7 chi2-be7, i2-kip8 cheng3 Chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 hak8-seng, lan2 kiam2 m7-si7 chin ai3 khoaN3 chit nng7, saN lang5 e5 bou5-iuN7; hoaN-hi2 put-si5 sim-sim liam7-liam7 ai3 kau3 Siong7-te3 e5 chhu3 mah? Lan2 chai lan2 lang5 e5 sim-sin5, jiok8-the2, put-si5 long2 u7 khiam3-khoeh, sou2-i2 lan2 e5 sim na7 chin khiam-pi, chhin-chhiuN7 sim-lai7 chin san3-hiong ai3 him-bou7 Siong7-te3 e5 gi7; ai3 thiaN Bok8-su, Thoan5-to7-su chhian2-beng5 Siong7-te3 e5 to7-li2, iuN2-chhi7 lan2 sim-sin5 e5 bi2-niu5 tit-tioh8 chiau5-pi7; ki5-kiu5, kam2-sia7, gim5-si, lan2 e5 sim kiam2 bo5 chin hoaN-hi2; hiong2-siu7 Siong7-te3 sou2 siuN2-su3 e5 bu5-han7 e5 hok-khi3 mah?
Ia5-sou ti7 se3-kan, tu2-chiah 12 hoe3 e5 si5, kap i e5 pe7-bu2 siong7 Ia-lou7-sat-leng2 siu2-poaN5 koe3-chiat; ti7 tian7-nih8 tui3 i e5 pe7-bu2 kong2: “Kiam2 m7-chai goa2 eng-kai ti7 goa2 e5 pe7 e5 chhu3 mah?” (Lou7-ka 2:49). Koh chit8-pai2, Ia5-sou iu5-goan5 kau3 Ia-lou7-sat-leng2, jip8 tian7, koan2 chhut tian7-lai7 be2-be7 e5 lang5, chhia-to2 in sou2 eng7 be2-be7 e5 khi3-ku7, lai5 chheng-khi3 seng3-tian7 e5 si5, ia7 bat kong2: “Kiam2 bo5 ki3-chai7 kong2, goa2 e5 chhu3 beh chheng cho3 ban7-bang ki5-to2 e5 chhu3 mah?” (Ma2-kho2 11:17)
(Tai5-oan5 Kau3-hoe7-po3 te7 517 koan3, 1928 ni5 4 geh8) 
